ne reckless and beautiful act, and be transformed for ever. Weaving together themes of love, loss, belonging, duty and human striving, Let the Great World Spin celebrates the effervescent spirit of an age and the small beauties of everyday life. At once intimate and magnificent, elegant and astonishing, it is a lyrical masterpiece from a storyteller who continues to use the wide world as his canvas. 0aElectronic books.2 acloudLibrary403Whole productuhttp://ebook.yourcloudlibrary.com:80/library/dekrook-document_id-oee88r901195nam  22002054  45000010014000000060019000140070015000330080041000480200018000890370012001070400028001191000025001472450053001722600043002253000011002685200579002796550022008587100017008808560092008979781408854518m    ||  d |      cr un|||||||||170506s2014||||||||||||s|||||||||||eng||  a9781408854518  aoefpyr9  aMnSpTMCLbengcMnSpTMCL1 aMcInerney, Jay.4aut10aBright Lights, Big Cityh[electronic resource] :  a[S.l.]:bBloomsbury Publishing,c2014.  a192 p.  aYou are at a nightclub talking to a girl with a shaved head. The club is either Heartbreak or the Lizard Lounge. All might become clear if you could just slip into the bathroom and do a little more Bolivian Marching Powder. Then again, it might not... So begins our nameless hero's trawl through the brightly lit streets of Manhattan, sampling all this wonderland has to offer yet suspecting that tomorrow's hangover may be caused by more than simple excess. Bright Lights, Big City is an acclaimed classic which marked Jay McInerney as one of the major writers of our time. 0aElectronic books.2 acloudLibrary403Whole productuhttp://ebook.yourcloudlibrary.com:80/library/dekrook-document_id-oefpyr901567nam  22002294  45000010014000000060019000140070015000330080041000480200018000890370012001070400028001191000025001472450049001722600034002213000011002555200897002665210019011636500024011826550022012067100017012288560092012459781407019666m    ||  d |      cr un|||